717265f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - [Broome Street]
717265f-a.text:
Lamport Export Company
507-511Broadway, Manbattan
Nederal Art Project
''Changing New York'
Berenice Abbott, photographer
Neg. No. 3
[Note: negative at Museum of the City ofNew York]
Code I A-3
Oct 7, 1935

717264f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - Broome Street
717264f-a.text:
(1)
Broadway, east side, north from Broome Street. Note the Broadway surface car
April 19, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTICNS.
(2)
A detail of same, showing Nos. 502-04, 306, 508, 510, 512 and 516
(right to left). No. 506, the first low building was an old Dodd-Mead
retail store site.
April 19, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(3)
A limited view, showing mainly No. 306.
April 19, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
